summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plats 76E and 76W of the Official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property between W. Barton and W. Trenton Streets and between 25th and 29th Avenues S.W. in Section 36, Twp. 24 N., R. 3 E., W. M. to Community Business (BC).
